-- CORRECT: Tysan Gets Buyout Offer from Group for HK$2.5b
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2013-08-19T03:37:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-19/correct-tysan-gets-buyout-offer-from-group-for-hk-2-5b.html
(Correct name of company in
headline.) Co. has received offer from buyout group for all
shares not already owned, according to a statement to the Hong
Kong stock exchange.
* Barclays Capital Asia assisting with deal
* Offer of HK$2.86/shr, a premium of about 10% to the last
closing price
* Group also offers to buy 2m outstanding options
* Offeror to fund buyout with equity commitments from Blackstone
Group
* Deadline for offer is March 31, 2014
